resources.string: Management will provide small bubbles and straw. By using straw you have to carry the bubble and place it in the cup. Distance and Time will be decided by the management. Who will Collect the more bubbles with in the time, that person is the final winner.
You people have to arrange all the letters in the correct places. There is not time limit for this game. Who will arrange in less time, that person is the final winner.

You People have to carry the balloon without touching with hands and without falling down. Once balloon fall down or blasted you have to start from the starting line. In this game 2 participants needed. Before participating you have to select one partner.
